After an order is processed, you will receive an email with tracking information, you can track your package using the links in the email. Tracking emails can take up to 24 business hours to send. <br><br>

If you place your order late in the day (after 2:30 PST) or the product is drop shipped from the manufacrurer, you may receive your tracking number the next day. If you haven't recieved tracking, please fill out this form and we will get it to you
